nguage=en_US&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" border=\"0\" src=\"\/\/ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/widgets\/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B00F3J9G1W&amp;Format=_SL250_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=avocadulife-20&amp;language=en_US\"><\/a><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/e\/ir?t=avocadulife-20&amp;language=en_US&amp;l=li3&amp;o=1&amp;a=B00F3J9G1W\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\">\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<style>.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col{border-top-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;}.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col,.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col:before{border-top-left-radius:0px;border-top-right-radius:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;}.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col{column-gap:var(--global-kb-gap-sm, 1rem);}.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col{flex-direction:column;}.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col > .aligncenter{width:100%;}.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col:before{opacity:0.3;}.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4{position:relative;}@media all and (max-width: 1024px){.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col{flex-direction:column;}}@media all and (max-width: 767px){.kadence-column_5fcb63-f4 > .kt-inside-inner-col{flex-direction:column;}}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-2 kadence-column_5fcb63-f4\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\"><style>.wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading_8f15ca-fa, .wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading_8f15ca-fa[data-kb-block=\"kb-adv-heading_8f15ca-fa\"]{font-style:normal;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading_8f15ca-fa mark, .wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading_8f15ca-fa[data-kb-block=\"kb-adv-heading_8f15ca-fa\"] mark{font-style:normal;color:#f76a0c;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;}<\/style>\n<h3 class=\"kt-adv-heading_8f15ca-fa wp-block-kadence-advancedheading\" data-kb-block=\"kb-adv-heading_8f15ca-fa\">Etekcity Digital Body Weight Bathroom Scale with Step-On Technology<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Staying fit and healthy is just a step away. Simply stepping on the large tempered glass platform and receive immediate results displayed on a sizeable backlit LCD display. Sophisticated sensors ensure that your results are within 0.1 lbs. Of whatever is being weighed, ensuring accurate weight measurement time after time.&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/3JeHgZa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">Click here.<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can purchase a variety of these online and they will provide a more accurate picture of your fat loss. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another way to determine fat loss is to calculate your body mass index.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Body mass index, also known as BMI, can be used to determine the amount of fat on your body.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The third way to determine the amount of fat on your body is a caliper. A <a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/424eVgT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">caliper<\/a> is an instrument that calculates the thickness of your fat in certain locations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/measuring-body-fat-percentage-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"weight Loss vs Fat Loss measuring body fat percentage\" class=\"wp-image-36163\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/measuring-body-fat-percentage-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/measuring-body-fat-percentage-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/measuring-body-fat-percentage-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/measuring-body-fat-percentage-150x100.jpg 150w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/measuring-body-fat-percentage.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ways to Promote Fat Loss<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our program, the <a href=\"https:\/\/programs.avocadu.com\/p\/21-day-fat-loss-challenge\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/programs.avocadu.com\/p\/21-day-fat-loss-challenge\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow sponsored\">21-day fat loss challenge<\/a>, is all about losing fat on our bodies while promoting healthy muscle mass and water weight.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best way to shed fat without losing the weight you need to keep is by adjusting your diet and nutrition. Many diets and fat loss programs will ask you to eat too little, which can be dangerous and unhealthy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our program is different as we don\u2019t ask you to eat less than what your body needs. We just ask you to adjust what you\u2019re eating &#8211; and not permanently either!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Where other programs want to strip you of key nutrients and restrict your calorie intake to dangerous levels, our program focuses on educating you on nutrients and minerals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We even offer a list of approved foods and non-approved foods so you won\u2019t have to guess at what will help you in the challenge.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You\u2019ll want to keep your protein intake high, as protein actually helps the body burn fat. Staying away from carbohydrates is another way to promote fat loss.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another great way to lose fat is by exercising.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Don\u2019t overdo it though, as overexercising can actually cause more harm than good.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/programs.avocadu.com\/p\/21-day-fat-loss-challenge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow sponsored\">The 21-Day Fat Loss Challenge<\/a> program focuses on two exercises to promote fat loss: daily walks and resistance-based circuit training. Both of these exercises help you burn fat without causing much stress on your body.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Lose-Weight-Quick-with-the-Avocadu-21-Day-Fat-Loss-Challenge-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Lose Weight Quick with the Avocadu 21-Day Fat Loss Challenge\" class=\"wp-image-35271\" width=\"824\" height=\"463\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Lose-Weight-Quick-with-the-Avocadu-21-Day-Fat-Loss-Challenge-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Lose-Weight-Quick-with-the-Avocadu-21-Day-Fat-Loss-Challenge-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Lose-Weight-Quick-with-the-Avocadu-21-Day-Fat-Loss-Challenge-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Lose-Weight-Quick-with-the-Avocadu-21-Day-Fat-Loss-Challenge-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Lose-Weight-Quick-with-the-Avocadu-21-Day-Fat-Loss-Challenge-150x84.jpg 150w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Lose-Weight-Quick-with-the-Avocadu-21-Day-Fat-Loss-Challenge.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 824px) 100vw, 824px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For a more detailed explanation of how to lose fat quickly, check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/programs.avocadu.com\/p\/21-day-fat-loss-challenge\/\" target=\"_blank\">21-day fat loss challenge<\/a>. We assure you that if you follow our guide, you will shed fat quickly, safely, and effectively.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not ready to dive in? That\u2019s okay too! You can try a taster of our 21-day fat loss challenge for free. <a href=\"https:\/\/freeguides.avocadu.com\/21dc-training-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\">Get it here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Weight-Loss-vs-Fat-Loss-1-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Weight Loss vs Fat Loss 1\" class=\"wp-image-36166\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Weight-Loss-vs-Fat-Loss-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Weight-Loss-vs-Fat-Loss-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Weight-Loss-vs-Fat-Loss-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Weight-Loss-vs-Fat-Loss-1-150x225.jpg 150w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Weight-Loss-vs-Fat-Loss-1.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If you\u2019ve found this article, it\u2019s safe to assume that you\u2019re interested in seeing the number on the scale go down. You may see a lot of programs out there offering rapid weight loss or rapid fat loss. The question is, what\u2019s the actual difference between losing weight vs losing fat? It can be confusing&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":18,"featured_media":36164,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_kad_blocks_custom_css":"","_kad_blocks_head_custom_js":"","_kad_blocks_body_custom_js":"","_kad_blocks_footer_custom_js":"","_kad_post_transparent":"","_kad_post_title":"","_kad_post_layout":"","_kad_post_sidebar_id":"","_kad_post_content_style":"","_kad_post_vertical_padding":"","_kad_post_feature":"","_kad_post_feature_position":"","_kad_post_header":false,"_kad_post_footer":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[25],"tags":[],"taxonomy_info":{"category":[{"value":25,"label":"Weight 